headline: US Plastic Market Poised to Grow from $195.37 Billion in 2025 to $266.15 Billion by 2033
summary: The US plastic market is projected to grow significantly, reaching $266.15 billion by 2033 from $195.37 billion in 2025, driven by a 3.94% CAGR. Key growth drivers include rising demands from packaging, automotive, and construction sectors, combined with advancements in sustainable plastic technologies and recycling strategies.
